</m:math>

</emphasis></para><para id="id208353"><emphasis effect="bold">Definition 3 (Sobolev regularity)</emphasis> <emphasis effect="italics">
<m:math overflow="scroll"><m:mtext>Let</m:mtext><m:mspace width="0.25em"/><m:mrow><m:mi>φ</m:mi><m:mo>:</m:mo><m:mtext>ℝ</m:mtext><m:mo>→</m:mo><m:mtext>ℂ,</m:mtext><m:mspace width="0.25em"/>

<m:mtext fontstyle="italic">then</m:mtext><m:mspace width="0.25em"/><m:mi>φ</m:mi><m:mspace width="0.25em"/><m:mtext fontstyle="italic">is said to belong to the Sobolev space of order s</m:mtext><m:mspace width="0.25em"/>


