of differentiability, it does yield lower and upper bounds on <m:math overflow="scroll"><m:mi>r</m:mi></m:math>,
the Hölder regularity, and hence the differentiability of
<m:math overflow="scroll"><m:mi>φ</m:mi></m:math> if <m:math overflow="scroll"><m:mrow><m:mi>φ</m:mi><m:mo>∈</m:mo><m:msup><m:mi>L</m:mi><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math>. This can be seen from the following inclusions:</para>
      <equation id="uid60">
        <m:math overflow="scroll" mode="display">
          <m:mrow>
            <m:msup>
