        <para id="id212728">Solving for <m:math overflow="scroll"><m:mrow><m:mi>μ</m:mi><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>k</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> in terms of lower order discrete moments and using
