        <para id="id212907">which allows calculating the even-order discrete scaling function moments
in terms of the lower odd-order discrete scaling function moments for
<m:math overflow="scroll"><m:mrow><m:mi>k</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mo>⋯</m:mo><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. For example:
</para><equation id="uid90">
